metadata.name: RarePass: Genesis #1
metadata.description:
Collect the very first RarePass, offered exclusively on SuperRare. Own a piece of history with artwork from up to 24 of cryptoart’s most celebrated and iconic artists. Curated by SuperRare Labs, creators of the world’s premier cryptoart marketplace. 

As a legendary patron of cryptoart, the buyer of RarePass: Genesis #1 receives: the first minted artwork from each of the monthly Airdrop Artist series; 1x item of the buyer’s choosing from every limited edition SuperRare Artist swag drop for the year; the signed, numbered, and uniquely marked skateboard #1 from the Other World limited edition swag drop; and a RarePass design like no other, uniquely styled by acclaimed 3D artist Alessio De Vecchi.

In addition to these special benefits, all RarePass: Genesis holders receive: a monthly artwork airdrop from 1 of 12 legendary artists; 3x opportunities per month to win unique 1/1 artworks; Exclusive Pass Holder Community access; and additional benefits to be announced.

Learn more at rarepass.superrare.com

*Must continue holding a pass to be eligible for pass #1 benefits, monthly airdrops & giveaways as they are released. Previously delivered benefits, airdrops, & giveaways are not transferable with pass #1 on the secondary market. Benefits apply for the 12 month RarePass: Genesis program. Learn more at rarepass.superrare.com
